Package: FBPostCleaner
Type: Package
Title: Cleans Facebook text posts to be used for sentiment analysis.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matthew Luu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matthew Luu <mluu1@usf.edu>
Description: This package preps Facebook text posts to be used for sentiment analysis. It cleans text and removes emojis using a regular expression that matches all unicode emoji characters. It replaces common abbreviations with their full forms using a list of abbreviations and their corresponding full forms. It also removes Facebook mentions and page tags using regular expressions that match the specific formats of these features on Facebook.
License: CC0 1.0 Deed
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
